      <title>富时指数将韩国和印度纳入债券基准指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/ftse-adds-south-korea-india-to-bond-benchmarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富时罗素 (FTSE Russell) 固定收益、货币和大宗商品指数政策全球主管 Nikki Stefanelli 解释了该公司为何决定将韩国纳入其基准债券指数，并将印度纳入其新兴市场债务指标。她在“彭博社；亚洲交易”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/ftse-adds-south-korea-india-to-bond-benchmarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 02:02:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Point72 将迁至东京办事处，扩大其日本业务范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/point72-to-move-tokyo-office-as-its-japan-footprint-expands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁史蒂夫科恩的 Point72 资产管理公司在东京的办公空间几乎扩大了一倍，目前该公司正搬迁至首都中央金融区的一座较新的摩天大楼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/point72-to-move-tokyo-office-as-its-japan-footprint-expands</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:46:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称加拿大 Couche-Tard 将对日本 Seven & I 的出价提高至 470 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/couche-tard-is-said-to-boost-seven-i-offer-to-47b-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，Circle K 连锁店的加拿大所有者 Alimentation Couche-Tard Inc. 向 7-Eleven 连锁店的日本所有者 Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 发出了 7 万亿日元（472 亿美元）的新潜在收购价格。Reed Stevenson 在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-09/couche-tard-is-said-to-boost-seven-i-offer-to-47b-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刺激措施疑虑和假期数据疲软导致中国股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对北京的刺激计划产生怀疑，且假日消费数据出现疲软迹象，中国在岸上市股票开盘下跌，抹去了周二的部分涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/chinese-stocks-slump-amid-stimulus-skepticism-weak-holiday-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 01:35:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：刺激计划担忧导致中国股市领跌亚洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济数据疲软且北京方面拒绝承诺采取更多经济刺激措施，中国内地股市周三领跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 22:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国债券市场改革后加入主要富时罗素指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/korea-joins-major-ftse-russell-index-after-bond-market-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国将于明年加入富时罗素的主要全球债券指数，这是其金融市场基础设施改革的最高水平，旨在吸引数百亿美元的外国投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/korea-joins-major-ftse-russell-index-after-bond-market-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 20:18:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代汽车计划在印度创纪录 IPO 中募资高达 33 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/hyundai-aims-to-raise-3-3-billion-in-record-india-ipo-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现代汽车公司寻求通过其印度子公司首次公开募股筹集最多 33 亿美元资金，开启该国有史以来最大规模的上市交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/hyundai-aims-to-raise-3-3-billion-in-record-india-ipo-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 11:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国节日消费落后于新冠疫情前水平，表明需要刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-consumer-spending-lags-pre-covid-era-shows-stimulus-need</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管有迹象表明，在政府最近推出一系列刺激措施后，游客支出正在趋于稳定，但周一结束的中国长假期间，游客的支出仍低于疫情爆发前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-consumer-spending-lags-pre-covid-era-shows-stimulus-need</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:19:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国市场警告习近平需要更多刺激措施推动经济反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-markets-warn-xi-that-more-stimulus-is-needed-to-fuel-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从国家主席习近平上个月试图为中国经济放缓划上句号以来，投资者一直强烈要求他采取强有力的财政刺激措施，支持货币宽松政策，以推动中国股市出现多年来最大的涨势之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-markets-warn-xi-that-more-stimulus-is-needed-to-fuel-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 09:45:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
